盖茨退出微软董事会，热衷研发新冠病毒快速检测工具。
Gates withdrew from Microsoft's board of directors and is keen to develop a new Crown Virus Rapid Detection Tool.
周源。
Zhou Yuan.
财经杂志                      。
Financial magazine.
财经杂志。
